vote.title: An ordinance granting a private license to EOSII At Highland Park Place, LLC, for the use of a total of approximately 685 square feet of land space to install, maintain and utilize an existing masonry retaining wall, a new masonry retaining wall, nine trees with uplights and landscaping on a portion of Cole Avenue right-of-way located near its intersection with Armstrong Avenue - Revenue: General Fund $2,614.00 annual fee, plus the $300.00 one-time fee and $20.00 ordinance publication fee
